<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Facture {{ invoice.number }}</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS épuré spécialement optimisé pour Dompdf (sans Bootstrap pour éviter les bugs de conversion) */
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .invoice-box {
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .header-table, .meta-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header-table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0d6efd;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .invoice-details {
            text-align: right;
        }
        .invoice-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }
        .number-badge {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .dates {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .actors-section {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .actors-section td {
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .client-card {
            border-right: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-right: 20px;
        }
        .object-card {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #777;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .items-table th {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #555;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .items-table td {
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 12px 10px;
        }
        .text-center { text-align: center; }
        .text-right { text-align: right; }

        .totals-table {
            width: 40%;
            float: right;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .totals-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .total-ttc {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0d6efd;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px dashed #dee2e6;
            padding-top: 20px;
            clear: both;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="invoice-box">

    <table class="header-table">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <div class="title">DevisPro</div>
                <div class="subtitle">Prestataire : {{ invoice.user.userIdentifier }}</div>
            </td>
            <td class="invoice-details">
                <div class="invoice-title">Facture</div>
                <div class="number-badge">{{ invoice.number }}</div>
                <div class="dates">
                    Date d'émission : <strong>{{ invoice.createdAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</strong><br>
                    Date d'échéance : <strong>{{ invoice.dueDate|date('d/m/Y') }}</strong>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <table class="actors-section">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <div class="client-card">
                    <div class="section-title">Facturé à :</div>
                    <strong>{{ invoice.customer.firstname }} {{ invoice.customer.lastname }}</strong>
                    {% if invoice.customer.company %}
                        <div style="color: #0d6efd; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 3px;">{{ invoice.customer.company }}</div>
                    {% endif %}
                    <div style="color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;">France</div>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td>
                <div class="object-card">
                    <div class="section-title">Objet / Référence :</div>
                    <div>{{ invoice.title|default('Prestation de services') }}</div>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <table class="items-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Description des tâches / produits</th>
                <th class="text-center" style="width: 60px;">Qté</th>
                <th class="text-right" style="width: 110px;">Prix U. HT</th>
                <th class="text-center" style="width: 60px;">TVA</th>
                <th class="text-right" style="width: 110px;">Total TTC</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {% for item in invoice.invoiceItems %}
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>{{ item.description }}</strong></td>
                    <td class="text-center">{{ item.quantity }}</td>
                    <td class="text-right">{{ item.unitPrice|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</td>
                    <td class="text-center">{{ item.vatRate }} %</td>
                    <td class="text-right" style="font-weight: bold;">{{ item.totalTtc|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</td>
                </tr>
            {% else %}
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="5" style="color: #777; font-style: italic;">
                        Détails des prestations globaux basés sur le devis d'origine.
                    </td>
                </tr>
            {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <table class="totals-table">
        <tr>
            <td>Total HT :</td>
            <td class="text-right"><strong>{{ invoice.totalHtAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Montant TVA :</td>
            <td class="text-right">{{ invoice.totalVatAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background-color: #e7f1ff;">
            <td class="total-ttc">Total TTC :</td>
            <td class="text-right total-ttc">{{ invoice.totalTtcAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Merci pour votre confiance. En cas de retard de paiement, une pénalité de 3 fois le taux d'intérêt légal sera appliquée.</p>
        <p style="font-weight: bold; color: #333;">DevisPro — Logiciel de facturation conforme.</p>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
